title: Premier Lincoln Park Upgraded High-Rise 1BD With Granite & Stainless!
posting_body: QR Code Link to This Post   Call Apartment Guys at 773-549-2474, ask about ID #71053. Upgraded Lincoln Park hi-rise one bedroom with granite and stainless!
